{"tid":2015881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李慧琼停內會 謀硬過國歌法","createTime":"2020-05-14T04:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T06:48:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8f480337c77f05c3b816962000d5310e0ebc2a6f","tid":2015881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200514/GBHYWEMEGQ5WZKZOQBAYTUQJVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200514%2FGBHYWEMEGQ5WZKZOQBAYTUQJVU%2F&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=62b60a47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200514%2FGBHYWEMEGQ5WZKZOQBAYTUQJVU%2F&h=f0c7220d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200514/GBHYWEMEGQ5WZKZOQBAYTUQJVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n李慧琼停內會 謀硬過國歌法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200514/large/1589386745_e9bf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200514%2Flarge%2F1589386745_e9bf.gif&h=a86fa04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李慧表示本周五不會召開內會，稱希望大家冷靜一下。何量鈞攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民建聯主席李慧琼上周五在立法會保安和法律顧問護航下成功「奪權」，強行召開特別內會會議後，李指周五將不會召開內會，希望「（民主派和建制派）大家冷靜一下」，並邀建制派「班長」廖長江和民主派會議召集人陳淑莊「傾一傾」，至於政府要求本月27日《國歌法》提交立會大會進行二讀，她會否再召開內會，李只說稍後決定。民主派質疑李不想開會，無非要繼續濫用主席權力，自行決定將《國歌法》交大會審議。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼受訪時稱，希望以「冷靜期」找出降溫方法，但她未有為重開內會定下日期，推說政務司長。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n之後再審議延長產假的法案。至於下次重開內會時。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n理，再作考慮，至於李是否需要為上周五內會的混亂情況負責，李重申不希望再有衝突混亂情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗轟無權決定議程<br />\n<br />\n對於李慧琼稱不召開會議是希望大家冷靜，主持內會選主席的公民黨法律界議員郭榮鏗反駁，他過去主持的會議，並無任何議員受傷及衝擊，不排除李可能在《國歌法》27日二讀前都不再開內會，以便繼續濫用主席權力，「市民要睇清楚，（李）呢啲就係真真正正的濫權、奪權」，重申立會討論議案次序應由議員在內會商討，「𠵱家佢（李）就當內會係佢嘅囊中物，自己決定晒所有嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n民主派會議召集人陳淑莊指，暫時未收到廖長江邀面談，但估計雙方縱會談亦不會有太大進展，重申李慧琼沒有權力決定內會議程，李做法只為向主持內會選舉的郭榮鏗「宣示主權」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙、何嘉瑤"},{"pid":"468fa66ac291cecfba66fe6576500aa767148086","tid":2015881,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c618b527c0a32722b5a45dc206845abedfc2be","tid":2015881,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"自己唔申請禁制令<br />\n講經咩"},{"pid":"c4e2a441cf6109846f85a85f7f6bcd930f99b99f","tid":2015881,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"自立為皇"},{"pid":"398d5156a36de72224a0eb986fc713320f6dec4a","tid":2015881,"uid":124180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"唔係好明點解郭榮鏗唔召開內會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02125377db804c1b5550192cb3bab8b2e336a380","tid":2015881,"uid":116554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"當日選擇行出會議室 又唔去JR 又唔申請禁令<br />\n講經咩"},{"pid":"50747c588d8dee11c6f20a32d0b15ebf3120b6cb","tid":2015881,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398d5156a36de72224a0eb986fc713320f6dec4a","tid":2015881,"uid":124180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"唔係好明點解郭榮鏗唔召開內會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"主席先有權"},{"pid":"cd9ff6543f9258097d142b8c779c133bb8fad8c5","tid":2015881,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50747c588d8dee11c6f20a32d0b15ebf3120b6cb","tid":2015881,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398d5156a36de72224a0eb986fc713320f6dec4a","tid":2015881,"uid":124180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"唔係好明點解郭榮鏗唔召開內會<